content.comment:
We thank all reviewers for their detailed feedback. We have uploaded a revised version addressing all of the concerns raised by the reviewers. Briefly, highlights of the major changes we made include: 
- Moved Algorithm 1 from Appendix C to Section 3;
- Added ImageNet class names in Section 3.1;
- Cited and discussed the papers mentioned by Reviewer 3 in Section 4; 
- Text revisions to improve readability. 
We also address individual reviewer comments below.

